### 核销券结算接口测试(商家端)
### 基础配置
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@token = YOUR_SHOP_TOKEN_HERE
@shopId = 1

### 1. 结算列表 - 全部
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/settlement/lists?shop_id={{shopId}}
token: {{token}}

### 2. 结算列表 - 待结算
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/settlement/lists?shop_id={{shopId}}&state=1
token: {{token}}

### 3. 结算列表 - 已结算
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/settlement/lists?shop_id={{shopId}}&state=2
token: {{token}}

### 4. 结算列表 - 分页查询
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/settlement/lists?shop_id={{shopId}}&page=1
token: {{token}}

### 5. 结算列表 - 店铺ID为空(应失败)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/settlement/lists
token: {{token}}

### 6. 结算详情 - 正常查询
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/settlement/detail?id=1
token: {{token}}

### 7. 结算详情 - 结算记录不存在
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/settlement/detail?id=99999
token: {{token}}

### 8. 结算详情 - ID为空(应失败)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/settlement/detail
token: {{token}}
